summary: My Re-placers by b117! I use SKYRIM NPC EDITOR and re textured some npcs!
descriptionHtml:
=======MY REPLACERS==========
1. INFO
2. CREDITS
3. COMPATIBILITY
4. INSTALL
5. UNINSTALL
6. EXTRA

1.INFO
I use SNE (SKYRIM NPC EDITOR) to re texture some npcs that i encountered during the game and thought they looked ugly. So i want to fix that!

2.CREDITS
ApachiiSkyHair by Apachii.(NEEDED IF YOU DONT WANT SOME NPCS TO LOOK BALD)
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10168
SNE (SKYRIM NPC EDITOR) by foretrenty for the help with editing the npcs.
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=4554

4.INSTALL
Extract all files from \"{name of file}\". Then move the stuff to:

\"C:/Program Files (x86)/Steam/steamapps/common/skyrim/Data\"

or

\"C:/Program Files (x86)/The Elder Scrolls Skyrim/Data\" i think.

5.UNINSTALL
Delete the files you placed in the \"Data\" folder.

3. COMPATIBILITY
Need 1 mod ApachiiSkyHair

6.EXTRA
SWE(SteamWorkshopEdition)ElisifOnly
http://bit.ly/MRElisifSWE
